---
title: Cheesy Mushroom & Bacon Fettuccine with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: This fettuccine dish pairs the earthy flavours of mushrooms with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the richness of the pasta with a sweet and juicy pear.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6674eac39deef291574f506f-a3f1263b.jpeg
